{"tid":493420,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[月供股票] 2017年12月","createTime":"2017-12-08T13:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T13:45:32.000Z","uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"15bdd2c093035f6628226628d5b83a7b79bb605e","tid":493420,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"朱千雪讓我哭巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未得閒開post，代開住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先 向間諜巴打致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢之前主要係教大家月供盈富基金(2800)<br />\n但由於仲未等到佢過黎<br />\n我決定開個月供股票先<br />\n因為知道好多巴絲都係月供幾隻(我自己都係)<br />\n<br />\n新手知識：<br />\n問：咩叫月供股票？<br />\n答：每月用你指定既金額，購買你指定既股票。<br />\n例：你set左月供$2000盈富、$2000騰訊、$2000匯豐，假設你用中銀黎做月供，會係每月既第十一日買入。假設盈富個日係$20一股，你會買到100股，騰訊係$201一股，你會買到9股，即$1809，銀行只會扣你$1809。<br />\n<br />\n問：月供股票有咩好？<br />\n答：1）低入場費：如果你睇好騰訊，但佢一手要大約兩萬蚊，但你冇咁多錢，月供就幫到你。你可以每月$5000咁供。2）平均成本：假設騰訊三個月既價係：$170、$180、$190，你同樣都係月供$5000，係第一個月你會買到29股，第二個月買到27股，第三個月買到26股，變相平個陣買多啲，貴個陣買小啲。個平均買入價會係$15000/(29+27+26)=$182.9。<br />\n<br />\n3）減低心理因素：由於每月都係指定個日入貨，我地唔需要睇價入，平時好多時會見佢貴，冇入到，點知就升到咩咁。<br />\n<br />\n問：啲碎股點算好？有冇息收？<br />\n答：係有息收的，唔需要草夠一手先有。至於會唔會賣唔出？中銀就承諾可以以正價沽出碎股，所以唔洗擔心。<br />\n<br />\n問：用邊間？收費如何？<br />\n答：主要都係推介呢兩間：中銀，一通。<br />\n中銀：可以用信用卡供，容易周轉，仲草埋積分。<br />\n每個月$50，已包收息費、存倉、買入，可以話係全包價<span style=\"color: red;\">包撚哂</span>。可以以正價沽出碎股。<br />\n<a href=\"http://bochk.com/m/tc/investment/securities/monthly.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbochk.com%2Fm%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Fsecurities%2Fmonthly.html&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0536ebdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bochk.com/m/tc/investment/securities/monthly.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一通：所有交易都係$5，收息每次$30。如果你月供3隻，每月就係$15。（有錯請補充，因為我用中銀的）<br />\n<br />\n問：有咩記數app?<br />\n答：Ticker。非常清晰咁記錄你既交易同會自動幫你計你個平均買入價。<br />\n<br />\n問：比較受歡迎既月供選擇？<br />\n答：盈富基金、騰迅、匯豐、建行、港鐵、煤氣、電能、港燈、領展。<br />\n<br />\n問：中銀幾號扣數，買入？<br />\n答：每月第十一日買入，第十日扣數，如果撞正非交易日，會順延。例如，十號係星期六，咁會下星期一先扣數，星期二買入，星期三出statement。<br />\n<br />\n問：中銀ebanking邊到睇買入價？<br />\n答：電子結單-&gt;證券交易<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先，其他留待其他巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一通幾錢一個月？收息點計手續費？聽講個SYSTEM成日壞？會唔會買唔到貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊間股票多選擇啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n渣打免佣好似抵啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n匯豐長期免手續費，唔係仲平咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排見南商做緊優惠？有無巴打知詳情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買夠10萬轉返去銀行得唔得？有存款保障？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後射去中銀收幾錢？中銀係咪免手續費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係全免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中銀信用卡供股可以儲積分？我上網搵唔到嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中銀信用卡嗰邊未見扣數？有無巴打扣咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但今日開咗張信用卡，今個月都會轉到用信用卡扣數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開戶要帶咩文件？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月供用邊間最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中銀用邊張信用卡供有優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用一通定中銀供抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家咁貴 月供係唔係好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲股市跌 月供係唔係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻股票唔會郁 月供係唔係賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中銀月供 點樣睇到買入平均價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">伸手黨懶人包Link</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"http://bfy.tw/FKYu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbfy.tw%2FFKYu&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5a752eca\" target=\"_blank\">http://bfy.tw/FKYu</a>"},{"pid":"e4ebb6bb1d25eec7d56f72801b22214c28aef2fc","tid":493420,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5d9e59eb992e8d1a20a5bb2f19f0660dc33a834d","tid":493420,"uid":13012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"中銀一個月 月供時間又到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等睇全日最高價位買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271a104207f40957643574783ab3db52eeb626c5","tid":493420,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f9e45a8c489f2707e35a1492b6d80fd9b45a01","tid":493420,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c023dd55fc638f41bbb1a3f494d0c5ca3fb4947","tid":493420,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"竟然爆post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b24996a0a088ebdac503a313ed1869bd633f7ad","tid":493420,"uid":150273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/493394/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/493394/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"6c96e331ae6e886aedb8193e94bd501dcaaa83f7","tid":493420,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco