 />\n巴打可能誤會左我意思 <br />\n我用緊中銀做月供<br />\n想供一隻銀行股"},{"pid":"06a585821499d51ddee285bb87010d79882749f8","tid":493420,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"中銀服務真好差，d 員工無 train 過咁"},{"pid":"53631dee98850f4cbb9ac55e5de707ca4ddf06a6","tid":493420,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3間銀行 中銀 HSBC 恆生 <br />\n大家會簡供邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你長遠睇好咩地方既經濟發展 大陸定英國定本地"},{"pid":"3afbaf5728b889d607b8d07d1b81b2d95dd04081","tid":493420,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲整左條link屌柒班伸手黨</blockquote><br />\n做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ecd15acffc4bdc4dfd607989a89d5aa7d00bc0","tid":493420,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>3間銀行 中銀 HSBC 恆生 <br />\n大家會簡供邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n睇你長遠睇好咩地方既經濟發展 大陸定英國定本地</blockquote><br />\n11都係大笨象旗下"}]}